cu.explanation_en: Setting local SCTP control port to 0 causes invalid port number, leading to F1 interface connection failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting tracking area code to 0 causes invalid TAC, leading to tracking area configuration rejection and mobility issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將追蹤區域代碼設定為 0 會導致無效的 TAC，造成追蹤區域配置被拒絕和移動性問題。
